@startuml
title Sequence — Ad Campaign → Lead Capture → Contractor Outreach

actor Visitor
participant "Google/Instagram/TikTok Ad" as AD
participant "Landing Page\n(Next.js on Netlify)" as LP
participant "Make.com\nCampaign Manager" as MAKE
participant "Airtable CRM" as AIR
participant "HubSpot CRM" as HUB
participant "Contractor Outreach\n(GMass/SendGrid)" as OUT

== Ad Click ==
Visitor -> AD: sees ad “Get masonry quotes now”
AD -> LP: redirect with UTM params

== Landing Page ==
Visitor -> LP: fills lead form {name, email, job_type, location}
LP -> MAKE: webhook POST new_lead + UTM params

== CRM Update ==
MAKE -> AIR: insert new record
MAKE -> HUB: create contact + deal (stage=Marketing Qualified)
MAKE -> AIR: tag source = ad_channel, location = GTA

== Outreach ==
MAKE -> OUT: auto-send contractor blast email
OUT -> Contractor: “New lead available in your area”

== Admin Visibility ==
MAKE -> HUB: log marketing campaign performance
MAKE -> AIR: update lead dashboard

@enduml
